msg: Paired with part of Karl's last change, treat a nonexistent base file
the same as an empty base file.  This ought to get checkouts working.
This is probably too relaxed for updates; if we're doing an update and
the base file is missing, we should report an error or go fetch the
version we expected.  But we can take care of that later.
